headline: New Family Ownership of Pak Mail in Cedar Park, Texas to Continue Offering Shipping and Office Services
summary: Annex Brands, Inc., a leading franchisor in the packing, shipping, and office services industries, is pleased to announce the successful transfer of ownership of an existing Pak Mail location in Cedar Park, TX, to new owner, CJ Wilson, and her family, Reginald Wilson, Jayce Wilson, and Joshua Wilson. This transition to new ownership ensures that the community will continue to benefit from the essential shipping and office services Pak Mail offers.

headline: Want $2,000 in Annual Dividends? Invest $11,000 in Each of These 3 Stocks
summary: The three stocks listed here each pay high dividends that yield more than 5%.  Generating high dividend income can be tricky, because you don't want to just load up on stocks with the highest yields.  It's important to carefully consider a company's financials and what lies ahead before relying on its dividend.
